<component type="desktop-application">
  <id>io.github.MarkusAureus.MediaCatcher</id>
  <name>Media Catcher</name>
  <summary>Download audio and video from various websites</summary>
  <summary xml:lang="sk">Sťahovanie audio a videa z rôznych webových stránok</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      Media Catcher is a user-friendly desktop application for downloading audio and video content from various websites including YouTube.
      It provides an intuitive interface with customizable themes and supports playlist downloads, subtitle extraction, and multiple quality options.
    </p>
    <p xml:lang="sk">
      Media Catcher je používateľsky prívetivá desktopová aplikácia na sťahovanie audio a video obsahu z rôznych webových stránok vrátane YouTube.
      Poskytuje intuitívne rozhranie s prispôsobiteľnými témami a podporuje sťahovanie playlistov, extrakciu titulkov a viacero možností kvality.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Download audio in various formats (MP3, WAV, AAC)</li>
      <li>Download video with customizable quality settings</li>
      <li>Support for playlists and individual videos</li>
      <li>Subtitle download with multiple language options</li>
      <li>Multiple themes for customization</li>
      <li>Progress tracking and download management</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

  <launchable type="desktop-id">io.github.MarkusAureus.MediaCatcher.desktop</launchable>
